<Body>
	<Title>广东河源55名学生疑集体食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008年11月28日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">27日</Time>，<Location lid="l1">河源市连平县上坪镇第二中学</Location>发生一宗<Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">疑似食物中毒</Denoter>事故</Event>，<Event eid="e2">该校<Participant sid="s2">55名学生</Participant>在<Location lid="l2">学校</Location>统一<Denoter did="d2" type="action">用</Denoter>过<Object oid="o2">早餐</Object>后</Event><Event eid="e3">发生集体<Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">疑似食物中毒</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　
    <Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e4">据<Participant sid="s4">当地政府有关负责人</Participant><Denoter did="d4" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5"><Time tid="t5" type="relTime">昨日上午</Time>，<Location lid="l5">连平县上坪二中</Location>有<Participant sid="s5">55名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d5" type="action">进食</Denoter>了校方提供的<Object oid="o5">一盘红萝卜</Object>和<Object oid="o5">鸡蛋炒粉丝</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e6"><Time tid="t6" type="relTime">昨天下午3时10分左右</Time>，<Participant sid="s6">这批学生</Participant>先后<Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>上吐下泻、腹痛、头晕等<Object oid="o6">现象</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Participant sid="s7">校方</Participant><Denoter did="d7" type="perception">发现</Denoter></Event>后<Event eid="e8">立即将<Participant oid="o8">55名疑似食物中毒的学生</Participant>急<Denoter did="d8" type="movement">送到</Denoter><Location lid="l8">当地医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e9"><Denoter did="d9" type="operation">抢救</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
     
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e10">经过医院<Participant sid="s10">医生</Participant>输液、催吐等<Denoter did="d10" type="operation">治疗</Denoter>后</Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Time tid="t11" type="relTime">昨晚</Time>已有<Participant sid="s11">部分学生</Participant>陆续<Denoter did="d11" type="operation">出院</Denoter></Event>，但截至<Event eid="e12"><Time tid="t12" type="relTime">昨晚8时35分</Time><Participant sid="s12">记者</Participant><Denoter did="d12" type="action">发稿</Denoter></Event>时止，仍有<Event eid="e13"><Participant oid="o13">20多名学生</Participant>在<Location lid="l13">医院</Location><Denoter did="d13" type="operation">观察救治</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e14"><Time tid="t14" type="relTime">昨晚8时30分</Time>，<Participant sid="s14">连平县政府</Participant>在<Location lid="l14">该县上坪镇</Location><Denoter did="d14" type="operation">召开</Denoter>全县食品安全紧急<Object oid="o14">会议</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e15"><Denoter did="d15" type="operation">部署</Denoter>有关地毯式清查各镇学校食品安全大<Object oid="o15">行动</Object>。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence>据介绍，<Event eid="e16">这次<Denoter did="d16" type="emergency">疑似食物中毒</Denoter>事故</Event>初步估计是<Event eid="e17">由于<Participant sid="s17">该校学生</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="action">进食</Denoter>了<Object oid="o17">变质食物</Object>所引发的</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e18"><Time tid="t18" type="relTime">昨晚</Time>，<Participant sid="s18">当地卫生监督所</Participant>、<Participant sid="s18">疾控中心</Participant>等部门正在<Denoter did="d18" type="operation">提取</Denoter><Object oid="o18">相关样本</Object></Event><Event eid="e19">进行<Denoter did="d19" type="operation">化验</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
